solution: ```class Solution {
    public int countKDifference(int[] nums, int k) {
        int[] freq = new int[101];
        int count = 0;
        for (int num : nums) {
            int up = num + k;
            if (up <= 100) count += freq[up];
            int down = num - k;
            if (down >= 1) count += freq[down];
            freq[num]++;
        }
        return count;
    }
}```
